name: Debra Morrison
offering: Business Consulting, Financial Coaches, Public Speaking
what_you_do: Debra L. Morrison is a financial coach and the Founder and Chief Navigating Officer of Women Navigating Finances, helping women navigate their financial journeys and avoid pitfalls while strategizing for wealth accumulation and retirement income.
who_you_serve: Debra serves women seeking guidance in financial planning and management, particularly those looking to accumulate wealth or manage their finances during retirement.
bio: Debra has over 40 years of financial expertise, holds a Master’s Degree in Retirement Planning, and is an Accredited Estate Planner.
